ply of the Zaporozhian Cossacks]]'', 1880-1891, [[State Russian Museum]], St. Petersburg\nFile:Surikov streltsi.jpg|[[Vasily Surikov]], ''[[:ru:\u0423\u0442\u0440\u043e \u0441\u0442\u0440\u0435\u043b\u0435\u0446\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u043a\u0430\u0437\u043d\u0438|Morning of Streltsy's execution]]'', 1881, [[Tretyakov Gallery]], [[Moscow]]\nFile:Entrada de Roger de Flor en Constantinopla (Palacio del Senado de Espa\u00f1a).jpg|[[Jos\u00e9 Moreno Carbonero]], 1888, ''The Entry of Roger de Flor in Constantinople'', [[Senate of Spain|Senate Palace]], [[Madrid]]\n</gallery>\n\n==See also==\n* [[Classicism]]\n* [[List of Orientalist artists]]\n* [[Painting]]\n* [[Cobweb painting]]\n*[[History of painting]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==References==\n*Barlow, Paul, [https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:9MoshlkHpFYJ:www.manchesteruniversitypress.co.uk/uploads/docs/s1_23.pdf+Paul+Barlow+Professor&hl=en&gl=uk&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESjcjev4zZWsyXRk2Qb0TAbQHs52uwq7cmMmRBnlY97ah2aGpKYtVsGu-QOIeMciCrUfH45N1knB0NFikusclJybCwP5TMoAMaQJNS8TPzZFOBvOQvtUrmEPUT--Kqw8tmhvKr8G&sig=AHIEtbSRK7DWVGwdLbYF38jvUAihfTFS0Q \"The Death of History Painting in Nineteenth-Century Art?\" PDF], ''Visual Culture in Britain'', Volume 6, Number 1, Summer 2005, pp.&nbsp;1\u201313(13)\n*[[Anthony Blunt|Blunt, Anthony]], ''Artistic Theory in Italy, 1450-1660'', 1940 (refs to 1985 edn), [[OUP]], {{ISBN|0-19-881050-4}}\n* Bull, Malcolm, ''The Mirror of the Gods, How Renaissance Artists Rediscovered the Pagan Gods'', Oxford UP, 2005, {{ISBN|0195219236}}\n*Green, David and Seddon, Peter, ''History Painting Reassessed: The Representation of History in Contemporary Art'', 2000, Manchester University Press, {{ISBN|9780719051685}}, [https://books.google.com/books?id=Q_m5y85mHzQC&pg=PA7&lpg=PA7&dq google books]\n*Harding, James. ''Artistes pompiers: French academic art in the 19th century'', 1979, New York: Rizzoli\n*Harrison, Charles, ''An Introduction to Art'', 2009, Yale University Press, {{ISBN|9780300109153}}, [