st-before/EP024994070008?aid=zap2it|title=Kim's Convenience Episode Guide|work=zap2it|accessdate=November 6, 2016}}</ref>\n |DirectedBy=James Genn\n |WrittenBy={{StoryTeleplay|s= Kevin White and Ins Choi|t= Anita Kapila}}\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2016|12|6}}\n |ShortSummary= Mr. Kim tries to prove that \"best before\" dates mean nothing when Janet objects to his selling expired ravioli; Mrs. Kim's serving up her homemade [[galbijjim]] at the church bazaar when a surprise visit by Jung forces her to admit that she's embarrassed by his troubled past.<ref name=\"before\"/>\n |LineColor=F7941E\n |Viewers=\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber=10\n |EpisodeNumber2=10\n |Title=Janet's New Job\n |RTitle=<ref name=\"NewJob\">{{Cite web|url=http://tvlistings.zap2it.com/tv/kims-convenience-janets-new-job/EP024994070010?aid=zap2it|title=Kim's Convenience Episode Guide|work=zap2it|accessdate=November 15, 2016}}</ref>\n |DirectedBy=Dawn Wilkinson\n |WrittenBy=Anita Kapila\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2016|12|13}}\n |ShortSummary=Janet is sick of working for free and finds a job at Handy Car Rental putting Jung in a difficult position when she notices that Jung and Shannon are attracted to each other; Appa hires Gerald to work in the store but Gerald is nervous and clumsy whenver Appa is around, which is all the time.<ref name=\"NewJob\"/>\n |LineColor=F7941E\n |Viewers=\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber=11\n |EpisodeNumber2=11\n |Title=Handyman\n |RTitle=<ref name=\"Handyman\">{{Cite web|url=http://tvlistings.zap2it.com/tv/kims-convenience-handyman/EP024994070011?aid=zap2it|title=Kim's Convenience Episode Guide|work=zap2it|accessdate=November 16, 2016}}</ref>\n |DirectedBy=Dawn Wilkinson\n |WrittenBy=Kevin White\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2016|12|20}}\n |ShortSummary=Mr. Kim fixes a broken toilet for Kimchee; Jung hides out with Shannon; when Edwin Carter ([[Kevin Bundy]]), an old acquaintance of Eomma's drops by, Janet believes there's more to his relationship 